-ndehanaiga
by mella » Sun 08.28.2011 4:56 am お前の気持ちも分からんではないがThis sentence has been translated "I understand how you feel" but the ending sentence is negative, isn't it?Tk you for your reply
mella
Posts: 19Joined: Mon 08.02.2010 2:42 pm
